{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 2508179, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Reignac", "body": "Aggramar was one of the titan Pantheon, and more specifically was Sargeras's lieutenant. The two of them fought the demons across the universe. Aggramar blessed [url=https://wow.gamepedia.com/Tyr]Keeper Tyr[/url] on Azeroth and was the titan who discovered Draenor, creating [url=https://wow.gamepedia.com/Grond]Grond[/url] to fight the [url=https://wow.gamepedia.com/Sporemound]Sporemounds[/url] - meaning he is ultimately the reason that orcs exist. When Sargeras decided that the only way to save the universe from being corrupted by the Void was to destroy everything, Aggramar tried to stop him. In fury and sorrow, Sargeras cleaved Aggramar in two.\n\nIn Legion, Sargeras brings Aggramar back as the first of his Dark Pantheon: the titans revived to serve the Legion.", "date": "2017-07-15T13:41:50-05:00", "rating": 46, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2017-07-28T18:33:55-05:00", 1, "Reignac"]}
